parameters: Yo, wassup! If you need some armor, you came
to the right place. I'm loaded with all sorts
of armors here for you to pick and wear!
Be a smart cookie, a wise chocolate cake,
Making games is a special type of passion.
You need to do everything, not just a little
bit with passion, or else it's not worth doing
I never make the same mistake twice. I make it
5 or 6 times, just to be sure.
The best kind of shield in combat is having
People ask me how I like my eggs.
Walking with a friend in the dark is better
than walking alone in the light.
The true value of an armor isn't how much it shines
but how much it can withstand a beatdown.
When you want something you've never had,
you have to do something you've never done.
